{"tid":893741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"博物館不怕你興奮流體液　男女全裸看裸體特展","createTime":"2018-11-08T00:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T09:06:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3d76788a5de9d9b46b8a47dbd0f435d367d976","tid":893741,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:51:37.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞的戈梅茲(Pedro Nel Gomez)博物館，近日舉辦一個裸體特展，除了展出已故畫家戈梅茲一生當中所創作的裸體畫，更讓參觀者、無論男女全裸入場參觀。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這個裸體特展名為「裸體、表現與自由」，展出戈梅茲在不同時期所創作的120幅裸體畫作，博物館也特地讓參觀者裸體入內。據悉開展當天有超過50人裸體參觀，他們可以盡情在博物館內解放流汗，興奮看名畫，或者被畫作感動而流淚。此外，這個特展的幕後協辦者，就是當地的一個天體團體「Otro Cuento」，該團體的會員有超過800人。<br />\n報導也指出，法國巴黎先前就曾有博物館舉辦「裸體特展」讓參觀者裸體入場的經驗，這次戈梅茲博物館也受到這股裸體風的影響，而決定為全裸男女開展。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181108/640_93d49cb220c463bbc347f75c88da7142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181108%2F640_93d49cb220c463bbc347f75c88da7142.jpg&h=c5fffbea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181108/640_8e256f5400515e1cdead986118ad81aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181108%2F640_8e256f5400515e1cdead986118ad81aa.jpg&h=2534d216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181108/640_38164263bb5f72953f603c437b65b618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181108%2F640_38164263bb5f72953f603c437b65b618.jpg&h=0d7f2d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181108/640_cd79c8281cae62f16a5de9fe4c8516f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181108%2F640_cd79c8281cae62f16a5de9fe4c8516f7.jpg&h=0e458fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181108/1462397/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181108%2F1462397%2F&d=xVjNWqMRx4GtcmlJECpyBv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=09bb2b81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181108%2F1462397%2F&h=9fd7c13d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181108/1462397/</a>"},{"pid":"21002f8fc5b285bc65abb535cc263f67c7d3c25b","tid":893741,"uid":35746,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"全男班，長頭髮既係達哥"},{"pid":"1c45b102c82b516853f793068422a14df3f86352","tid":893741,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21002f8fc5b285bc65abb535cc263f67c7d3c25b","tid":893741,"uid":35746,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"全男班，長頭髮既係達哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a636fc665c1685ab431f8403ebd4cc380cabfb","tid":893741,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:09:07.000Z","msg":"屌你得個背脊 仲要打埋格仔"},{"pid":"677c83a8bee40fabff683565fcc4f22b9c590d27","tid":893741,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:11:40.000Z","msg":"入去格劍"},{"pid":"b58b1d1ec9170c79aa829184c95a18fefcc92746","tid":893741,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:13:15.000Z","msg":"最後幅圖冇打格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe5e44c6f8cd34d2a6d603dc506f5995f359164","tid":893741,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21002f8fc5b285bc65abb535cc263f67c7d3c25b","tid":893741,"uid":35746,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"全男班，長頭髮既係達哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"所以佢咪比人當女人咁屌"},{"pid":"77ae5c